cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this artifact, please cite the MBPriorQ paper and artifact release."
title: "MBPriorQ Artifact Evaluation"
type: software
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-07-15"
license: Apache-2.0
abstract: >-
  Artifact for the MICRO 2026 paper Software-Hardware Co-Design of Prior-Aware
  W4A4 Micro-Block Quantization for Robust LLM Inference Across Model Families.
  It provides a representative Qwen3-0.6B accuracy reproduction, central
  ablations, and open SpinalHDL/Verilator functional validation of MBPriorQ's
  hardware mechanisms.
keywords:
  - large language models
  - post-training quantization
  - W4A4
  - FP4
  - hardware accelerator
  - artifact evaluation
